Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:11.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Catch your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:15.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,East, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.35,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you ever seen an adventurer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:22.04,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a rumor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:27.62,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,that an adventurer younger than me skipped \Nright over this mountain, humming a tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.44,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,If I could be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:31.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What can they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Can they live as one with the land?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:39.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Adventurers create nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:41.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They simply fight and shed blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:44.95,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:56.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That looks bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:58.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We have to tell the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:41.27,Default,Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:51.27,Inventory,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H612F2E&}The Big Bath \N{\c&H3D31AC&}Akihabara Town Baths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.27,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:54.35,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we should all come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:03:00.90,Title,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1843,1)}An Invitation from Eastal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:00.16,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,An Invitation from Eastal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.01,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Head-splitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:11.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:13.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.17,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Purification Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.19,SignD,,0000,0000,0000,,Death
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:19.38,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Assassinate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:21.38,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Aura Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.66,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai have a long cool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:33.90,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes, after casting a spell, \Nthey can't move afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:37.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it in my head, but I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.79,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro asked us to look after you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.54,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll be cracking down on ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.74,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:44.74,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:45.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:48.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,First, Tohya, as men, we can talk about p—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:50.93,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,"P"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:51.89,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.88,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.23,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I said we'd crack down on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't teach you much about \Nshrine priest techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.13,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.87,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,He told me everything I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.57,SignA,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.81,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.52,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Were you up all night again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, I slept a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.21,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.58,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,You should go out for a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:22.78,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Akihabara is changing so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.78,SignB,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Steam Engine-Equipped Vessel \N{\c&H85EFF9&\3c&H241B9F&}Ocypete
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.78,SignC,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Under \NConstruction!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:27.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to, but I have more \Nthings I need to look into.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:29.98,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,You mean a way to get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.61,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:34.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But if we're to live in this world, \Neven if only for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,we'll need knowledge and information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.04,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:42.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If a cook prepares food himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:45.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,or a crafter creates something himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they can make things that didn't \Nexist in the world of {\i1}Elder Tale{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:54.52,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,So you're trying to see if you can use \Nyour scribing skill for anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:58.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to draw up a simple contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I could use it for other things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.02,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:06.66,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I can't handle this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.12,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:08.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.88,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go! I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.66,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat! I want to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She called all of you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.93,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.04,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.29,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.55,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Summer has come to this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.34,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And summer is all about the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:28.68,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Snow cones, watermelon, ramen, \Nand curry rice at the beach, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.51,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go! I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.60,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat! I want to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.60,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:37.64,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The Crescent Moon Alliance is one of \Nthe Round Table's eleven guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.16,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,And you're its guild master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.94,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Akihabara still has a lot of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.86,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave it right now, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:50.56,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've worked really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.64,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still working really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:53.74,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I have
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:56.58,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,some fun once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.05,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come down, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:01.59,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the lady is the one \Nwho needs a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.16,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The beach, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:08.31,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:09.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,A new quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:15.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,"Round Table-Sponsored Training \NCamp for New Players"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:22.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A summer training camp for \Nnew players under level 40?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the stage that's been set for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:35.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,At last, it's time for everyone to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:38.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,the magnificent name of Rundel Haus Code!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:42.28,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,This is a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:45.21,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect excuse for a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.89,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The beach! Training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.51,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:52.16,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Round Table was talking \Nabout training new players.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:54.01,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Two birds with one stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:59.50,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,For Dark Shiroe, coming up with \Na plan like this is no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.71,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good Dark Shiroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.91,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,And you, as well, Naotsugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:06.91,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,"As well"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.03,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be going, Serara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:11.36,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.53,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.79,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I shall attend as one of the trainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.59,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,She's so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe and all his friends will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.70,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:37.60,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Part of me always blamed myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.81,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,For not being able to do anything for Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.36,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:48.15,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,But that's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:53.16,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I must make Shiroe think he did the right thing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:56.52,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,when he saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's biting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where the training \Ncamp will be held, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:18.19,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Choushi, in the Zantleaf region.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.45,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Karashin has already gone \Nand looked at the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:24.35,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,and has spoken to the People of the Land there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.60,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.99,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shouryuu, of our guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Rezarick, from the Black Swords, \Nwill be participating as trainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.49,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Now all I need is sunscreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.06,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The camp is next month, Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:43.83,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I have a summer dress for you, Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.83,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.70,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's getting overexcited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come on, try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.08,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.97,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find sunscreen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:54.47,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, there are weird people outside town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:57.88,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.85,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Was there an event like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.47,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:02.84,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.49,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:07.86,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've seen him somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.36,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They're all People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.86,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:18.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So are they.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:23.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I am a messenger of Sergiatte Cowen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:27.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,High Lord of Eastal's League of Freedom Cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:32.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I request an audience with \Nthe Round Table's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:36.80,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,In {\i0}Elder Tale{\i1}, Japan is called Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:40.06,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's divided into five major territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:46.02,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The League of Freedom Cities of Eastal is an \Nalliance of lords that rule Eastern Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:50.77,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Eastal has now made contact with the Round Table.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:55.28,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,They've asked for our participation in \Na meeting of the lords next month,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.56,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,and have invited us to a dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:02.41,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Did you anticipate this, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:07.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The People of the Land should be \Nwell aware of the Round Table.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I expected them to make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:14.20,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were prepared \Nto grant titles of nobility...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.26,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's a difficult question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,As is whether to participate in the conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.30,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If we participate, we can make connections \Namong the People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:29.56,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to learn things we \Ndon't yet know about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.48,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,And the demerits?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chance we may get \Ncaught up in their politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:39.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't participate, \Nthat possibility goes away, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:42.99,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,We lose a chance to gain valuable information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:44.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's the trade-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.24,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a chance of war with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:49.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:57.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Generally speaking, they are far \Nweaker than we adventurers are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:01.10,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you have in mind, Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:17.19,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell the salt air.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.90,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's so different from Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Minori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:29.88,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this area is primarily fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:30.62,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Those look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:37.76,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take them without asking, Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem with commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.03,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:46.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're as lively as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.89,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Isuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:52.36,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,In the real world, you'd never think of \Nholding a training camp within a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:58.90,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Is she one of the People of the \NLand that live around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:11.96,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:15.22,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we'll be staying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.89,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we'll have a barbecue in the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:21.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Shiroe could've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:22.65,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:27.30,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,He has an important conference \Nwith the People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.78,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,He has to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:33.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the training camp is going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:37.69,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm leaving my steam engine to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.91,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay focused, strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.20,Default - flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:48.84,Default - flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should attend the meeting \Nto gather information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:51.27,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,So they're going to give us titles of nobility?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.78,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,As though they're better than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:55.92,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,They're only non-player characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.90,Default - flashback,Ro,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't mere NPCs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.80,Default - flashback,Ro,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we understood that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:02.97,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.32,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,It's just habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:09.92,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we're all in agreement about \Nattending the conference of lords?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.63,Default - flashback,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,So who's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:16.10,Default - flashback,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,That day overlaps with the training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.69,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in charge of that training camp, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.66,Default - flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose Crusty would be first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.84,Default - flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Round Table's representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.75,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:30.87,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,Which means someone from the \Ncrafting guilds should also go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:35.72,Default - flashback,Ro,0000,0000,0000,,We're working on the Ocypete...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.52,Default - flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,And I have many other projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.35,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting to the good part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.94,Default - flashback,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,At times like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.47,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:46.47,Default - flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.11,Default - flashback,Ro,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.49,Default - flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Michitaka will be happy to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.72,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.98,Default - flashback,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'd like to have one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:14:00.49,Default - flashback,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Someone skilled in bureaucracy \Nand information analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:04.42,Default - flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.42,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.70,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd wanted, you could have \Ngone to the training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja must follow her master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And why is Henrietta here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:21.25,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I'm participating as an observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And what's sticking out of your magic bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.57,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Just some fabric...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:29.79,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It most definitely isn't Akatsuki's summer dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.68,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,She followed me to get to Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.14,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,A pretty girl on each arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:43.14,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of information are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Everything we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:49.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But especially information about \Nthe People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.16,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.89,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When {\i1}Elder Tale{\i0} was a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the People of the Land were set to be \Nfar less powerful than adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:03.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,There were exceptions, such as the \NPrecursors and the Royal Guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:06.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,but generally, their levels and combat abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,never rose above a certain limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:13.32,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,If adventurers die, we revive at the Cathedral,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.11,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,but the People of the Land die for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:21.80,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But since the Apocalypse, the People \Nof the Land have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.91,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to drag you along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:26.91,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:32.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,For one thing, they aren't simple \Nnon-player characters anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:37.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But for another, you used to \Nreceive requests from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,known as quests, and then \Nitems for completing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:43.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The magic bag is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:48.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be the reward for one \Nof the basic quests everyone does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:55.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If the People of the Land's change means \Nno one can do that quest anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:16:01.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,New players who don't have \Na magic bag yet never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The effect will be bigger than we imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:08.13,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell Marie about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.86,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Information?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.98,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Shiro asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:20.44,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,He said to "talk to the People of the Land \Nand learn as much as you can."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:22.71,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you spoke to the village elder?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:27.38,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.50,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.33,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe asked you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.51,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have to do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.60,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.62,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.48,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like patting you on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.70,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I-It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.51,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We've finished our greetings, so let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.70,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:01.46,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:03.06,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,That's something only a warrior could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:03.91,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.34,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:10.00,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, have you stretched enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:14.26,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,If you underestimate the sea, \Nbad things can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:17.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you just can't swim, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.22,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.14,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:26.40,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,My beautiful swimming has been \Ncompared to a leaping dolphin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.36,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Beho—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.40,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.03,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.07,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, um, the information...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.03,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Later, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.59,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer! Swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.76,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:49.39,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:53.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir... It's so fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.67,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,About two hours from the city of Akihabara,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.27,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,where southern Tokyo would \Nbe in the real world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:03.93,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,where Hamarikyuu Park would sit, \Nis the Palace of Eternal Ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:13.43,HUD1,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}The Palace of Eternal Ice{\fs18}\NJapan Server \NLeague of Freedom Cities, Eastal/ Bay Area \N No Monsters \NNo PVP \NSkill Use Permitted \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NEvents/ None Currently
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:12.38,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,A palace with foundations of magical ice, \Ncreated by a dead race of ancient Alvs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.05,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,...nerve-wracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:50.95,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of everyone around as \Nmonsters, and you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:54.42,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's only you, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:56.44,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:19:00.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look... w-weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:02.95,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.86,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You look cute! Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:08.54,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Like some kind of fluffy strawberry something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.33,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I want to order you for takeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:12.96,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,No, I {\i1}will{\i0} order you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:14.85,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,She stated that like a fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.82,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,She definitely followed Akatsuki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.26,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:24.40,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to conceal my weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:28.70,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you keeping that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:35.11,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty calm yourself, Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.24,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,A hero of his caliber
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:41.61,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,has no problem escorting two \Nladies to a big ball like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:42.83,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:47.24,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,A fancy ball like this is nothing for Dark Kuroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:49.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Kuroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:53.33,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:56.67,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I am Sergiatte Cowen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:02.80,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I am the coordinator for the \NLeague of Freedom Cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.27,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.99,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real nobleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:07.19,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.83,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:15.35,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,I am Crusty, the representative for \NAkihabara's Round Table Conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.30,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,He has guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:20.23,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Crusty looks like a nobleman himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I am Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:28.44,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sergiatte Cowen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:32.67,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,lord of the largest eastern city, \Nthe capital city of Maihama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:37.37,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful person in Eastal, \NLeague of Freedom Cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.36,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:47.43,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,So these guilds are like nobility \Nwithout lands of their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.99,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,and the powerful guilds rule the city \Nthrough discussion and debate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:56.47,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,So it resembles the way we run \NEastal, but on a smaller scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:58.01,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:04.82,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,But that means bestowing a noble \Ntitle upon only one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.63,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,would cause needless friction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:13.32,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, we're attracting a lot of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:15.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But no one's talking to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:18.51,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Out of respect for Sergiatte?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:24.74,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My guess would be that, just as we lack \Ninformation about People of the Land,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:28.30,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,they also lack information regarding us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:31.07,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,So they're wary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.74,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,They want information about us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:38.05,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,but they must be very careful \Nthat the conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:40.11,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't reveal too much about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:43.36,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:52.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So that's a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:56.25,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,That's my granddaughter in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:58.09,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,She is quite beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:21:59.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What is her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.21,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Lenessia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:12.61,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And tomorrow, for party training, \Nwe'll be going to a dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:15.16,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,A dungeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.94,0:22:18.72,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the Forest of Lagranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:22.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:25.49,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,However, it will only be you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:29.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Only us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:31.64,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:36.00,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe Memo \N\N{\fs20}The basics of combat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:09.21,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,A bountiful banquet is also
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:12.22,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,a place of politics, where opposing groups collide.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:14.80,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,The nobles try to gain control \Nof the adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:18.24,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,And Shiroe and the Round Table \Nare forced to negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.24,0:24:22.90,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Minori, Tohya, and their \Ncompanions face a harsh reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.90,0:24:30.99,Title,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,The Forest of Lagranda
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.29,0:24:25.02,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Forest of Lagranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.45,0:24:27.97,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Always look thirty seconds ahead.
